snippet.title: Froggo's Adventure: Drifting Sky - Early Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/3297850/Froggos_Adventure_Drifting_Sky/

Froggo's Adventure: Drifting Sky is another Simple retro 2D Platformer about Froggo on a side-scrolling adventure. Froggo had multiple dreams about adventuring in the sky and seeing some kind of mysterious figure. Wondering if any of these dreams have any meanings, Froggo goes on an adventure high above the clouds to seek an answer...

Note:
This trailer consists of early gameplay footage and most of the things shown are subject to change.
